## Limitations

The findings are based on available data and expert opinions, which may not fully capture the diverse experiences of all nursing home residents. The rapidly evolving nature of the pandemic means that new information and strategies are continually emerging. Additionally, the focus on specific geographic regions may limit the generalizability of the findings to other areas. Further research is needed to assess the long-term mental health impacts and the effectiveness of implemented strategies.